No. —, Original.

Ex parte: In the Matter of Rose Weiss, as Next Friend, etc., Petitioner. Submitted November 13, 1922. Decided November 20, 1922. Miss Rose Weiss for petitioner.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of habeas corpus herein denied, without prejudice to the right of the petitioner to apply for a writ of habeas corpus to the District Court of the United States for the Western District of Washington directed to the officers in charge of the McNeil Island Penitentiary.
